
SETUP
-------------------------------------------
follow steps https://golang.org/doc/install

clean
-----
rm -rf /usr/local/go

install
-------
download golag tar - https://golang.org/doc/install
tar -C /usr/local -xzf go1.11.linux-amd64.tar.gz

configure
---------
edit .bash_profile & write following line
  export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin
  source ~/.bash_profile

binaries for vim-go ":GoInstallBinaries"

RUN
-------------------------------------------
go run hello.go
go build hello.go

